    {
      "id": "f307c993-5976-4eea-be85-433c0b772d7e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "While working with real Udacity data, authors show that GritNet outperforms Logistic Regression in the overall task of predicting student success. Moreover, the differences are more pronounced in the first few weeks of the course.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "f307c993-5976-4eea-be85-433c0b772d7e",
        "parent": {
